Relationship between Prices and Apartment features

Bedrooms and Accomodations Rooms with bed tyoe as couch has more price per night as compared to the airbed. Also from the box plot of bedrooms vs price, we can say that accomodation with bedrooms 1,6,9,10 has highest average price but for 1 & 6, the interquartile range is wide which means that the prices vary as per time/season but if we check for rooms with bedrooms 9 or 10, there is a very narrow variation in prices throughout the timeline.

From the Accomodation box plot, we an see that with increase in the number of people to accomodate, there is an increase in average price trend which is also high for accomodations with 1 or 2 people. The reason for this price hike may be due to the inlusion of price increase during events or some special occasions.Number of beds show the same trend as in acomodations.
